  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When they exchanged the governments, and the Germans started to come in and the Russians started to escape, and Lida burned one piece of fire, and we had to hide behind it-- somewhere in a village-- not in the city because it was very tragic-- he was already much closer with Sonia.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They never married.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] said they married.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They never married.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was his girlfriend, and he was her boyfriend, but they never married.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they went to a peasant's-- to a farmer's house to stay over the few days that Lida was-- will be brought back to order.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so did we, but we went separately.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then he decided, Tovia, to go to see what's doing by his parents in [INAUDIBLE], and he took her along.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But I knew him before she knew him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She accidentally met with him at the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But she tried through me to accomplish all that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it was very, very tragic for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But at that time, like I said before, we were young.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were very nice to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had in Lida very late a ghet-- not a ghetto-- but before the ghetto, we had certain streets.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were divided to streets that, this is your part where you have to live.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it wasn't a closed ghetto, you understand?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I could move around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After a few days they quiet down and the Germans started to-- to come in to-- to take over Lida.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very much damage.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Most of the city was gone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The major streets was gone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Completely covered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We left Lida.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We walked to the farmer's houses behind Lida in the villages.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there we stayed over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You think they were so happy to keep us?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
